6411 - Insurance Agents, Brokers and Service Summary > ALLIANZ AUSTRALIA WORKERS' COMPENSATION (NSW) LIMITED is an Australian public company. Its operations cover insurance agents, brokers and service. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. ALLIANZ AUSTRALIA WORKERS' COMPENSATION (NSW) LIMITED is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by director Brendan Joseph Dunne. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $37.44 million. ALLIANZ AUSTRALIA WORKERS' COMPENSATION (NSW) LIMITED forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
